 The meeting reached a consensus after discussing the issue of fully surveying and discovering and compiling the unique national linguistic heritages created and developed by the Koreans for 5,000 years and solving all the issues on the principle of achieving the great national unity and giving full play to the national character of the Korean language in the idea of �gBy our nation itself�h, the main spirit of the June 15 North-South Joint Declaration. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
